description: The prop 'tabs' is an array of Tab items.
The prop 'styles' is an optional object for custom styling.
'isActive' is a Tab object that represents the currently active tab in the tabs list.
'setIsActive' is a dispatch function allowing the tabs component to update the active tab state.
'tabsState' is an array of Tab objects representing the complete state of tabs at any given moment.
'setTabsState' is a dispatch function for updating 'tabsState'.
